name: Cyclone  (CYCLONE.WAD FROM CYCLONE.ZIP)
description: The Ultimate Deathmatch level. Play single or co-op if you want, too; there are plenty 'O monsters. (Demons, Spectres, etc.) If you make it thru this on your own in U.V.with no cheats, please e-mail me so I can put you in the Cyclone HoFame! This level has been EXTENSIVELY playtested in modem and network play, and as my friends say : "Let's go 'round again!". I seem to remember one night where 4 of us were playing and we all had 30+ frags before we realized the sun had just risen, much to our surprise...
